In Css box model is a box wraps that aroind every single elemen in html.

That contains content,padding,border,margin.

div{
    height: 20px;
    width: 20px;
    border: 20px solid red;
    margin: 10px;
    padding: 5px;
    background-color: blue;
    box-sizing: border-box;//it makes the border and everything part of the heighjt width we get a small size
}

Margins is from the page.
border is the border in the element
padding the space between the border and the wrapped element.
